05:40.173 --> 05:44.553
<i>good for chopping,</i>
<i>like a machete type of weapon.</i>

05:44.553 --> 05:48.098
<i>My plan is to take pieces</i>
<i>of the 15N20,</i>

05:48.098 --> 05:51.643
<i>sandwich in the bigger piece</i>
